hello world (root) --

This example consists of a file and a script which can be copied up to remote host via drist with elevated privilages.

Option 1 (while inside the `hello_world_root` directory):

        # drsit -e ACME

Option 2 (from outside the `hello world_root` directory):

        # drist -e -F ./path/examples/hello_world_root/files/test.drist -S ./path/examples/hello_world_root/script ACME
